# More info: https://docs.docker.com/engine/reference/builder/#dockerignore-file
# Whitelist approach - only include what's needed

# Exclude everything
**

# Include Go modules
!go.mod
!go.sum

# Include source directories
!cmd/
!api/
!internal/
!pkg/
!hack/

# Exclude test files
**/*_test.go
**/testdata/
